extends base

block content
  p Hello,
  p You are receiving this email because you (or someone else) has requested a password reset for your account.
  p Please click the button below to reset your password:
  p
    a.button(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Reset Password
  p If you did not request this, please ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.
  p This link is valid for 10 minutes.
  p If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:
  p= url
